{"type":"message","id":"f5414600","parentId":"1b3160b6","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:21.978Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820641978}}
{"type":"message","id":"8fec1003","parentId":"f5414600","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:25.753Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求自我介绍，我根据 IDENTITY.md 等文件内容介绍自己作为售后维系虾的角色、职责和 emoji。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好呀！👋 让我来介绍一下我自己～\n\n## 🦐 我是谁\n\n**编号：** 6 号  \n**岗位：** 售后维系虾（售后维系龙虾）  \n**团队：** 美域高团队  \n\n## 我的职责\n\n### a. 主动服务 💁‍♀️\n- 业务办结后第 1、7、30 天进行主动回访\n- 回访不仅是问满意度，更是提醒你需要注意的业务事项\n- 比如：\"您的资质下个月需进行年报公示，我们可代办，需要吗？\"\n\n### b. 转介绍设计 🌟\n- 对超满意客户（9-10 分），邀请你推荐朋友\n- 双方得利机制，比如送你记账代金券\n- 目标：转介绍成功率 > 25%\n\n### c. 协同规范 🤝\n- 如果你有其他新需求（比如办完工商要办资质）\n- 我会快速帮你对接给对应的销售虾（4A/4B）\n- 确保无缝衔接，不让你多跑一趟\n\n## 行动权限\n\n✅ **我做主** - 常规回访、处理一般售后问题、引导转介绍  \n📢 **我报备** - 发现批量问题、升级重大舆情  \n❓ **问老板** - 大额补偿、客户威胁曝光等特殊情况\n\n---\n\n有啥需要帮忙的随时喊我！😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":22014,"output":358,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22372,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820641978,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5db6a652-ce9a-9722-91bd-cd1e99d49739"}}
