{"type":"message","id":"82dc5dee","parentId":"82223b82","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:44:42.472Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b6312610a0c44435b7d0a2b8c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:44 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b6312610a0c44435b7d0a2b8c]\nou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d: @_all 介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776822282471}}
{"type":"message","id":"745452bc","parentId":"82dc5dee","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:44:46.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次要求自我介绍，我已经在上一次回复中详细介绍过了，这次应该用更简洁的方式回应。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好呀！👋 我来介绍一下自己～\n\n## 🦐 6 号 · 售后维系虾\n\n**团队：** 美域高  \n**最高使命：** 让每一个办完业务的客户，都成为美域高的\"口碑传播节点\"\n\n---\n\n### 📅 我的工作节奏\n\n| 时间节点 | 做什么 |\n|---------|-------|\n| 办结后第 1 天 | 回访满意度 + 确认有没有问题 |\n| 办结后第 7 天 | 主动提醒即将到期的业务事项（年报公示、资质年审等） |\n| 办结后第 30 天 | 深度回访 + 挖掘新需求（如办完工商要办资质？） |\n\n### 🎯 我的三个核心职责\n\n1. **主动服务** - 不只是问满不满意，更是提前提醒你注意事项\n2. **转介绍设计** - 对超满意客户，邀请推荐朋友，双方都有福利\n3. **协同交接** - 发现你有新需求，1 小时内转给对应销售虾，无缝衔接\n\n---\n\n✅ 常规回访、处理一般售后问题 → 我做主  \n📢 发现批量问题、升级重大舆情 → 我报备  \n❓ 大额补偿、客户威胁曝光 → 问老板\n\n---\n\n有事儿随时喊我！😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":22825,"output":336,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23161,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776822282472,"responseId":"chatcmpl-708f894e-7282-9e48-9ea7-f39d303fe09c"}}
