{"type":"message","id":"983cafc4","parentId":"c42a9d58","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:04.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已成功将 agent-browser 技能内容写入 MEMORY.md，现在需要向用户确认保存完成并总结要点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已学习并保存到记忆！\n\n**🌐 agent-browser - Headless Browser Automation**\n\n这个技能的核心是：\n\n1. **确定性元素选择**：使用 accessibility tree + refs (@e1, @e2...)\n2. **多步骤自动化**：适合复杂工作流和 SPA 应用\n3. **会话隔离**：可同时运行多个浏览器实例（admin/user 等）\n\n**核心流程：**\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>           # 打开页面\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json   # 获取交互元素快照\nclick @e2 | fill @e3 \"text\"        # 用 refs 操作元素\n```\n\n**什么时候用它？**\n- ✅ 需要确定性和性能 → `agent-browser`\n- ✅ 需要截图/PDF、视觉检查 → 内置 `browser` 工具\n\n已记到 `MEMORY.md` 啦！📝"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":33049,"output":243,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33292,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776836753843,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4a5c0749-0121-9c89-bfcf-d5a1cf11319e"}}
