{"type":"message","id":"ee7b770a","parentId":"7915a2d7","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:47:14.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文件编辑成功后，需要向用户确认已学习并保存 skill-finder-cn 技能的详细信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已学习并保存到记忆！\n\n**🔍 Skill Finder - 技能查找器**\n\n这个技能帮助用户发现和安装 ClawHub 上的 Skills。\n\n**核心功能：**\n- 当用户问\"有什么 skill 可以 X\"时，自动搜索 ClawHub\n- 展示搜索结果（描述、下载量、Stars、是否已安装）\n- 推荐最合适的 Skill\n- 帮助安装并验证\n\n**工作流程：**\n1. 理解用户需求 → 提取关键词\n2. `clawhub search \"<关键词>\"` - 搜索\n3. 列出相关 Skills（带统计数据和安装状态）\n4. 推荐 → 安装 → **验证安装** ✅\n\n**常用命令：**\n```bash\nclawhub search \"<需求>\"    # 搜索\nclawhub inspect <name>     # 查看详情\nclawhub install <name>     # 安装\nclawhub list               # 查看已安装\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/  # 检查是否成功安装\n```\n\n**关键要点：安装后必须验证！**\n检查 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md` 是否存在。\n\n已记录到 MEMORY.md！📝"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":41880,"output":306,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42186,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776840428836,"responseId":"chatcmpl-78032b57-6f63-93e1-89fb-2a476e8b0445"}}
