{"type":"message","id":"3a3d4526","parentId":"7eb7c99a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:13:19.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了 reset 命令，我需要执行重置操作。根据 OpenClaw 的工作方式，reset 可能意味着清空当前的对话上下文状态或重置某些配置。我应该礼貌地确认这个操作并询问用户是否真的要进行重置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到 reset 指令！🔄 \n\n你是想：\n\n1. **重置对话记忆** - 清空当前会话的上下文？\n2. **重置我的身份/设定** - 重新初始化 AGENTS.md、SOUL.md 等配置？\n3. **重置某个具体技能的状态** - 比如清理 working-buffer、session-state 等？\n4. **其他含义** - 请说明具体想做什么\n\n请告诉我你要进行哪种 reset，我会按要求执行！😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":52842,"output":202,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53044,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776849194577,"responseId":"chatcmpl-837e37df-c0ce-9d85-82c9-afe8d892ab0d"}}
